    'By selecting associated categories, you are choosing to share the categories between shops. Once associated between shops, any alteration of this category will impact every shop.' => 'Seleccionant categories associades, podeu compartir categories entre diferents botigues. Si modifiqueu una categoria associada, modificareu les botigues que la tinguin associada.',
